  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "The ***protagonist*** is the [character](./character.md) whose [conflict](./conflict.md) drives the narrative — the person whose problem the story exists to explore. The protagonist is not necessarily the hero, not necessarily likable, and not necessarily the [narrator](./narrator.md). They are the character whose choices and consequences give the story its shape.",
